Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.21,0:28:01.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.59,0:28:12.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.26,0:28:14.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}Tell me what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.71,0:28:19.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.21,0:28:21.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}Looking for the escape from pain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.94,0:28:26.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.47,0:28:29.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.97,0:28:33.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.80,0:28:37.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.23,0:28:40.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.63,0:28:44.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}May be it's already too late to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.43,0:28:49.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.61,0:28:50.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}Ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.83,0:28:54.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:29:03.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0\fs57}It's not enough It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.02,0:29:08.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:11.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}we'll make it in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.52,0:29:17.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.09,0:29:19.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fsp0}I know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.21,0:28:01.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}命運帶我們走到了這裡 見識我的豪賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.59,0:28:12.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}仿佛落入了謊言的烈火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.26,0:28:14.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}請告訴我 你想讓我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.71,0:28:19.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}為了保護我所在的家園
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.21,0:28:21.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我尋找著逃脫苦難的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.94,0:28:26.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我握拳祈禱不會有人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.47,0:28:29.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我保證過不會放棄你和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.97,0:28:33.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}做好準備 直面必將到來的侵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.80,0:28:37.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}追趕著腦海裡浮現的倩影
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.23,0:28:40.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}捨棄掉孤獨戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.63,0:28:44.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}想奪回一切也許為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.43,0:28:49.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}但也不要丟失命運給你的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.61,0:28:50.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.83,0:28:54.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}如果我能改掉錯誤 救你於水火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:29:03.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}那也不夠我去打破這個世界的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.02,0:29:08.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我不會再丟下你 不會再失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:11.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我們一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.52,0:29:17.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我決不後退 決不成為別人理想的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.09,0:29:19.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我知道我該過怎樣的人生
